\c 15
\s Dare paJerusarema pamusoro pokudzingiswa nokuchengeta murairo waMozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino vamwe vakaburuka vachibva Judhiya vakadzidzisa hama \add vachiti\add*: Kana musingadzingiswi netsika yaMozisi, hamungaponeswi.
\v 2 Naizvozvo Pauro naBhanabhasi vakava nokupesana kusati kuri kuduku, nokuita nharo navo, vakazotenderana kuti Pauro naBhanabhasi navamwe vavo vakwire Jerusarema kuvaapositora navakuru pamusoro peshoko iri.
\v 3 Naizvozvo vakaperekedzwa nekereke, vakagura neFenike neSamaria, vakataura zvokutendevuka kwavahedheni; vakaitira hama dzose mufaro mukuru.
\v 4 Zvino vakati vasvika Jerusarema, vakagamuchirwa nekereke navaapositora navatariri, vakarondedzera zvose zvakaitwa naMwari achivashandisa.
\v 5 Asi kwakamuka rimwe bato redzidziso yavaFarisi vaitenda, richiti: Zvinofanira kuti vadzingiswe nokuvaraira kuti vachengete murairo waMozisi.
\v 6 Ipapo vaapositora navatariri vakavungana pamwechete kuti varangane pamusoro peshoko iri.
\v 7 Zvino nharo huru dzakati dzavapo, Peturo akasimuka akati kwavari: Varume hama, munoziva kuti kubva pamazuva apfuura Mwari wakandisanangura pakati pedu, kuti nomuromo wangu vahedheni vanofanira kunzwa shoko reevhangeri, vatende.
\v 8 Zvino Mwari muzivi womoyo wakavapupurira, achivapa Mweya Mutsvene, sekwatirivo;
\v 9 haana kuisa mutsaukovo pakati pedu navo, achinatsa moyo yavo nokutenda.
\v 10 Naizvozvo zvino munoidzireiko Mwari, kuisa joko pamitsipa yavadzidzi, rakanga risingagoni kutakurwa namadzibaba edu kana nesu?
\v 11 Asi tinotenda kuti isu tinoponeswa nenyasha dzaShe Jesu Kristu, nomutovo mumwe navo.
\v 12 Ipapo chaunga chose chikaramba chinyerere; chikateerera vana Bhanabhasi naPauro vachirondedzera zviratidzo nezvishamiso, zvakaitwa naMwari achivashandisa pakati pavahedheni.
\v 13 Zvino vakati vanyarara, Jakobho akapindura achiti: Varume hama, teererai kwandiri:
\v 14 Simiyoni warondedzera kuti waMwari kumutsa vahedheni sei pakutanga, kuti atore kwavari vanhu vezita rake.
\v 15 Namashoko avaporofita anobvumirana naizvozvi; sezvazvakanyorwa \add zvichinzi\add*:
\v 16 Shure kwaizvozvi ndichadzoka, ndivakezve tabhenekeri yaDhavhidhi, yakawira pasi; ndichavakazve matongo ayo, ndichaimisa;
\v 17 Kuti vakasara vavanhu vatsvake Ishe, navahedheni vose vanodamwa nezita rangu ndizvo zvinoreva Ishe unoita zvinhu zvose.
\v 18 Anozikamwa kuna Mwari mabasa ake ose kubva pakuvamba kwenyika.
\v 19 Naizvozvi kugura kwangu kunoti: Ngatirege kutambudza avo pakati pavahedheni vakatendevukira kunaMwari;
\v 20 asi tivanyorere kuti vabve pazvakashatiswa nezvifananidzo, novupombwe, ne zvakadzipwa, neropa.
\v 21 Nokuti Mozisi kubva pamazera ekare, waiva navanomuparidza paguta rimwe nerimwe, achirabwa mumasinagoge sabata rimwe nerimwe.
\v 22 Zvino zvikaonekwa zvakanaka navaapositora, navatariri, nekereke yose kuti vatume varume vakasarudzwa pakati pavo, kuAndiyokiya pamwe chete naPauro naBhanabhasi, naSirasi, vakuru pakati pehama.
\v 23 Vakanyora noruoko rwavo, \add vachiti\add*: vaapositora navatariri nehama, kuhama dzokuvahedheni paAndiyokiya, neSiria, neKirikia; kwaziwai.
\v 24 Sezvatakanzwa kuti vamwe vakabva kwatiri vakakunetsai namashoko, vachidziyanisa mweya yenyu vachiti mudzingiswe nokuchengeta murairo, ivo tisina kuvaraira;
\v 25 zvaonekwa zvakanaka kwatiri taungana nomwoyo mumwe kuti titumire varume vakasarudzwa kwamuri, vadikamwa vedu Bhanabhasi naPauro;
\v 26 vanhu vakapira vupenyu hwavo nokuda kwezita raShe wedu Jesu Kristu.
\v 27 Naizvozvo tatuma Judhasi naSirasi, ivo vachataurawo vamene izvozvi nomuromo.
\v 28 Nokuti zvakaonekwa zvakanaka kuMweya Mutsvene nokwatiri, kuti tirege kukutakudzai mutoro mukuru kunze kwezvinhu izvi zvakafanira,
\v 29 Kuti murege zvakabayirwa zvifananidzo, neropa, nechakadzipwa, novupombwe; kana mukazvidzora pazviri, muchaita zvakanaka. Sarai zvakanaka.
\v 30 Zvino vakati vaendeswa, vakasvika Andiyokiya; vakavunganidza chaunga, vakavapa mwadhi.
\v 31 Ivo vakati vairava, vakafara zvikuru pamusoro pokunyaradzwa.
\v 32 Judhasi naSirasi, vaiva vaporofita vamene, vakakurudzira hama namashoko mazhinji, noku\add va\add*simbisa.
\v 33 Vakati vambogara kwenguva, vakaendeswa nehama murugare kuvaapositora, vakaenda kunavakanga vavatuma.
\v 34 Asi zvakaonekwa zvakanaka naSirasi kuti asarepo.
\v 35 Pauro naBaranabasivo vakagara Andiyokiya, vachidzidzisa nokuparidza shoko raShe, navamwe vazhinjivo.
\s Pauro naBhanabhasi vanoparadzana
\p
\v 36 Zvino mamwe mazuva akati apfuvura, Pauro akati kunaBhanabhasi: Ngatidzokerezve tindoshanyira hama muguta rimwe nerimwe matakaparidza shoko raShe, tivone kuti vakadini.
\v 37 Zvino Bhanabhasi wakanga achida kutora Johwanivo, wainzi Mako, kuti afambe naye;
\v 38 asi Pauro wakafunga kuti hazvina kunaka kumutora afambe nave, iye wakambovasiya paPamufiriya, akasaenda navo kubasa.
\v 39 Kukauya kupesana kukuru pakati pavo zvokuti vakabva vaparadzana, nokudaro Bhanabhasi akatora Mako, akaenda Saipuresi nechikepe;
\v 40 asi Pauro wakasarudza Sirasi; akabuda akenda, aiswa panyasha dzaShe nehama;
\v 41 akagura neSiria neKirikia, achisimbisa kereke.
